Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.63,0:00:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This doesn't seem to be it either, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.76,0:00:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We still have a long way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.68,0:00:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're just gonna have to\Ncross them all off, one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.93,0:00:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. Okay, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.39,0:00:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely no pushing\Nyourself too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.15,0:00:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.81,0:00:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing, I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.69,0:00:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato-senpai and Julis\Nshould be battling about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.82,0:00:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to give it my all, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.20,0:00:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's the spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.00,0:02:10.75,ArcName,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Scrambling
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.50,0:02:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sorry to keep you waiting, everybody!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.92,0:02:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There are now only two more matches\Nleft in the Phoenix Festa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.75,0:02:16.88,Sign Center NB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}AYATO AMAGIRI\NJULIS-ALEXIA VON RIESSFELD{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.75,0:02:16.88,Sign Right NB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}ERNESTA KUHNE\NCAMILLA PARETO{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.75,0:02:16.88,Sign Left NB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}DOROTEO LEMUS\NELLIOTT FORSTER{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.80,0:02:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who will vie for supremacy\Nagainst Arlequint in tomorrow's final?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.43,0:02:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Will it be Seidoukan\Nor will it be Galahadworth?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.30,0:02:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was used to this\Nfeeling of powerlessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.85,0:02:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I just can't take it this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.48,0:02:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For now, let's just have faith in Saya\Nand Kirin, and focus on our match.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.15,0:02:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right... I hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.74,0:02:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, then, the Galahadworth team...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.90,0:02:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}First... ranked #12\Ndespite being in junior high!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.37,0:02:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The young prodigy,\Nalso known as Claimh Solais...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.70,0:02:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Elliott Forster!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.87,0:02:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His teammate is Rank #11,\NDoroteo Lemus, a.k.a. Brightwen!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.17,0:02:59.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is his third Festa.\NHe's a seasoned veteran!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.18,0:03:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd prefer to get this match\Nout of the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.18,0:03:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but since we're up against Galahadworth's\NTrue Knights, that's not happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.10,0:03:10.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that, but this time\Nyou can't even use the Ser=Versta.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.94,0:03:13.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, about that...\NI'll figure something out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.07,0:03:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then, I'm leaving Forster to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.24,0:03:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take on Lemus!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.45,0:03:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.66,0:03:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Phoenix Festa Semifinal Match #2!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.70,0:03:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Battle start!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.67,0:03:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Burst into bloom, Amaryllis!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.76,0:03:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.77,0:03:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Glühen Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.77,0:03:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, well!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.35,0:03:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where did this armor come from?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.02,0:03:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right, it was generated\Nby Lemus's powers.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.48,0:03:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's highly protective,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.15,0:04:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and it's also a headache because it repairs\Nitself as soon as you destroy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.32,0:04:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.61,0:04:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not to mention, the armor's even\Nprotecting the school badge, too!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.17,0:04:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you're going all-out from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.92,0:04:21.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm up against the Glühen Rose herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.22,0:04:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why wouldn't I be?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.93,0:04:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.15,0:04:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Julis...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.06,0:04:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was your opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.40,0:04:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato Amagiri...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.61,0:04:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've been looking forward\Nto battling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.07,0:04:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you wouldn't keep me waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.53,0:04:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.79,0:04:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, where's your Ser=Versta?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.66,0:04:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you're not holding back on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.33,0:04:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, something came up,\Nand I can't use it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.71,0:05:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.42,0:05:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see those sword skills\Nthe student council president's mentioned!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.52,0:05:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That's weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.77,0:05:16.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've never shown that move\Nin this tournament before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.19,0:05:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.86,0:05:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you're skilled at counterattacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.69,0:05:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That first strike was a decoy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.74,0:05:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess I'd have to say that it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.82,0:05:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But be warned\Nthat counterattacks aren't...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.54,0:05:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...my only weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.02,0:05:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you're just as good\Nas you say you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.15,0:06:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Based on talent alone,\Nyou might be a match for Kirin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.57,0:06:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That goes without saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.32,0:06:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But that sword of yours is...\Nstill too light!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.61,0:06:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not in terms of power, but resolve!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.87,0:06:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As if I'd let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.08,0:06:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Amagiri Shinmei Style...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.96,0:06:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Twin Demon Bees!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.21,0:06:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}AMAGIRI SHINMEI STYLE\NTWIN DEMON BEES
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.43,0:06:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Elliott Forster... badge broken!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.77,0:06:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.48,0:06:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Burst into bloom...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.86,0:06:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Primrose!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.00,0:07:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Riessfeld can only go on the defensive\Nagainst Doroteo's lance charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.29,0:07:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We really should be astounded\Nby Doroteo's powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.71,0:07:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Creating such a complex image\Nand moving it so smoothly...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.22,0:07:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come out, Loropetalum!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.74,0:07:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Burst into bloom, Anthurium!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.50,0:07:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I wouldn't have it any other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.47,0:07:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Burst into bloom...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.05,0:07:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Longiflorum!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.40,0:08:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like my lance got to you first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.66,0:08:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Whoa, whoa!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.03,0:08:17.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}What are we supposed to make of this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.91,0:08:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Most likely, though Lemus's armor\Nwas able to protect him from the flames,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.46,0:08:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it couldn't block their heat, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.75,0:08:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning that he's been fighting\Nwhile being roasted?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.97,0:08:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.38,0:08:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What a reckless man you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.43,0:08:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, since I wanted to end this quickly...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.14,0:08:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, charging right into a wall\Nof flames is going too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.94,0:08:46.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I just took a gamble and lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.27,0:08:48.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.98,0:08:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on,\Nget it over with, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.24,0:08:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Doroteo Lemus... badge broken!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.03,0:09:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Winners, Ayato Amagiri\Nand Julis-Alexia von Riessfeld!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.27,0:09:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Another dead end.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.56,0:09:25.02,Sign Left Mid,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AYATO AMAGIRI
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.06,0:09:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.35,0:09:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Saya, how's it going over there?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.77,0:09:30.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. We still don't have\Nany real clues.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.82,0:09:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see. We're going to get ready\Nto head over as soon as we can.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.40,0:09:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning... it's over already?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.74,0:09:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah, thanks to you guys,\Nwe made it to the final. Thanks!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.04,0:09:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All right, can you send me that map?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.08,0:09:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.67,0:09:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad to hear that our senpais\Nwere able to advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.67,0:09:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In Ayato's case, that's a given.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.42,0:09:55.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So next is the final?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.14,0:09:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's going to be tough\Nfor even Ayato
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.85,0:10:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to beat those two\Nwithout the Ser=Versta.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.89,0:10:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're probably right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.81,0:10:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We've got to find Flora\Nbefore the final starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.90,0:10:13.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saya?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.53,0:10:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's so frustrating.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.99,0:10:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.09,0:10:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go. There's still something\Nwe can do right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.05,0:10:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.89,0:10:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saya and Kirin say they still don't have\Nanything to go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.06,0:10:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.35,0:10:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}TODAY'S MATCH HAS FINISHED\NFINAL MATCH WILL START AT NOON TOMORROW
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.61,0:10:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow's final starts at noon,\Nso that gives us
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.07,0:10:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,another 18 hours, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we factor in the inspection\Nbefore the match...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.24,0:11:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that gives us even less time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.45,0:11:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's join the search!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.16,0:11:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yo! Congrats on making the final...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.58,0:11:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.42,0:11:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's going on?\NWhat's with the gloomy vibe?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.79,0:11:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... There's a reason for that, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.71,0:11:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If there's anything I can do,\NI'll be happy to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.60,0:11:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.18,0:11:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.06,0:11:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just as the president suspects,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.19,0:11:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it's probably a sure bet\Nthat Dirk Eberwein's behind all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.32,0:11:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know a lot\Nabout Grimalkin, Yabuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.40,0:11:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.53,0:11:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to secrecy,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.82,0:11:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,they're better than all the other academies'\Nintelligence-gathering organizations.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.08,0:11:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.58,0:11:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather not get mixed up\Nwith those guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.04,0:11:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But this is a special case,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.71,0:11:53.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and if you're only out to find\Nthis Flora kid, I'll help you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.79,0:11:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, of course that'll be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.63,0:11:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd almost rather\Nyou didn't have a hand in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.26,0:12:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for that... at least,\Nthat's what I'd normally say,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.76,0:12:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but as a lightweight regular student,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.01,0:12:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather have\Na little more insurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.64,0:12:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see, that guy's number...\NI know I saved it in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.94,0:12:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care, but if it's going to take long,\Nwe're going to go on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.31,0:12:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. Well, I'm going to do\Neverything I can,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.94,0:12:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but don't count on me too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.95,0:12:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.28,0:12:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Julis, I'd like to investigate\Nanother avenue myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.24,0:12:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Another avenue?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.04,0:12:29.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fine by me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.08,0:12:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but I think you'd be wasting\Nyour time asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.21,0:12:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's a long shot, but I'd like to ask\Njust for the sake of asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.63,0:12:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows, we might get\Nsome kind of clue out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.35,0:12:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.77,0:12:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't turn around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.77,0:12:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. But you didn't have to\Ngo out of your way to meet me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.73,0:13:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.15,0:13:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way could we have\Ndiscussed that over a call!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.95,0:13:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.03,0:13:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.70,0:13:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So let me get straight to the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.62,0:13:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing I can tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.87,0:13:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.12,0:13:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get the wrong idea, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.83,0:13:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like they asked me to be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.00,0:13:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Actually, it's the opposite.\N- Opposite?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.55,0:13:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't really think the Tyrant wouldn't\Nguess you'd contact me, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.59,0:13:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, I haven't received\Nany kind of memo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.10,0:13:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, the information I have\Nwouldn't do you any good...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.06,0:13:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and he knows it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.44,0:13:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.57,0:13:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... I shouldn't have bothered you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.82,0:13:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hold up, Amagiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.61,0:13:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that I have no information.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.36,0:13:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I can still speculate, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.62,0:13:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Speculate?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.08,0:13:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You said you've narrowed your search\Nto the Redevelopment District, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.50,0:13:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.33,0:13:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, you'd probably be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.13,0:14:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But since we're talking\Nabout a kidnapping, I wouldn't bet on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.63,0:14:03.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.01,0:14:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm not mistaken,\Nthat place is a hotbed for criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.22,0:14:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why the Police Unit is always\Ncoming around to patrol the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.39,0:14:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a good place
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.89,0:14:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,for crimes like kidnapping\Nwhere you need to lay low long-term.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.90,0:14:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, Grimalkin\Nis all about working solo,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.53,0:14:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so they want to avoid the hassle\Nof dodging an investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.82,0:14:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case,\Nwhere would she be?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.87,0:14:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.49,0:14:34.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But the place that would\Ngive you guys the most trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.91,0:14:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My guess would be Rotlicht.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.83,0:14:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.17,0:14:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In the Redevelopment District,\Nyou could search as you wish,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.42,0:14:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but in Rotlicht, both legal\Nand illegal shops are clustered together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.05,0:14:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't just barge\Ninto one of those places, could you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.51,0:14:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But then someone would\Nhave to be in on it with Grimalkin,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.72,0:14:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,since they work solo, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.23,0:15:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah, since money talks\Nin that place as long as you pay up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.24,0:15:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, Camilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.91,0:15:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How about snapping\Nout of that bad mood?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.92,0:15:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We might've lost instead\Nif we hadn't used you-know-what.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.10,0:15:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You knew that yourself\Nfrom the start, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.23,0:15:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You and I are striving\Nfor different things, Camilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.90,0:15:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your final goal is "Ultimate Universality."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.65,0:15:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, a weapon\Nthat can be wielded by anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.66,0:15:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,By any kind of person at all, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.91,0:15:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.16,0:15:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But no such weapon exists in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.71,0:16:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So we're going to create beings\Nthat can wield weapons, puppets,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.96,0:16:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that humans will only\Nhave to issue orders to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.42,0:16:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Such puppets have no need\Nfor a will of their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.72,0:16:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, they shouldn't\Nhave a will, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.05,0:16:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.97,0:16:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So what I want is to produce autonomous\Npuppets that can cry, laugh and grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.93,0:16:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For them to gain the same rights\Nas humans one day, that's my goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.28,0:16:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember\Nthe day we first met?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.33,0:16:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. How could I ever forget\Nanything with that degree of impact?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.04,0:16:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.34,0:16:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When my parents' workplace was attacked\Nby anti-government forces...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.51,0:16:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The guards were decimated\Nin the blink of an eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.34,0:16:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My parents tried to fight back,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.89,0:17:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but there was no way civilians could\Nhold their own against trained warriors.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.98,0:17:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Half of my body is the body\Nof a puppet you made for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.53,0:17:54.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so I swore to you\Nthat I'd give you half of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.74,0:17:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That it was yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.95,0:17:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, you gave it to me, all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.53,0:18:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So... I have no intention\Nof criticizing your dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.83,0:18:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I admit that we have different goals,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.33,0:18:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but that's another story!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.17,0:18:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then why are you so mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.25,0:18:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is my rage as an engineer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.26,0:18:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was too dangerous\Nto put into practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.43,0:18:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But if we'd lost then,\Nit would've been game over for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.55,0:18:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You must have\Nenough results by now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.72,0:18:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My only goal is to win it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.27,0:18:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And then I'm going to have AR-D\Nand RM-C accepted as students here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.69,0:18:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If that happens, see, people will embrace\Nautonomous puppets, more and more!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.78,0:18:36.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.95,0:18:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.74,0:18:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am very sorry to trouble you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.62,0:18:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but there's something\NI'd like you to do for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.79,0:18:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.71,0:18:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering if you could possibly\Nleave this scar carved into my face, as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.80,0:18:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, that's not a problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.93,0:18:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But why would you ask for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.97,0:19:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Needless to say,\Nas proof that I fought this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.26,0:19:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You mean it's a badge of victory?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.85,0:19:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing as grand as that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.11,0:19:15.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have learned various things\Nthrough this particular battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.95,0:19:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What I perceived after exposing\Nmy own imperfections...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.03,0:19:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,this wasn't purely\Na matter of learning data,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.54,0:19:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but what humans call...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.62,0:19:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... growth!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.37,0:19:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I believe I achieved actual growth!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.59,0:19:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I want to leave behind proof of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.67,0:19:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prodigious!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.51,0:19:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me he's aware\Nof his own growth?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.56,0:19:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Master, I, too,\Nhave a favor to ask of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.93,0:19:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... you, too, RM-C?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.94,0:19:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When I transfer limit control to AR-D...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.02,0:19:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.19,0:19:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It would help if you could\Nnarrow the range a bit more
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.65,0:19:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,when my external armor is detached,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.19,0:20:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,or adjust it somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.53,0:20:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As it's humiliating...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.70,0:20:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The thing is,\Nsince there are technical issues, see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.79,0:20:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it can be done\Nin time for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.00,0:20:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Understood, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.30,0:20:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we can thank Saya Sasamiya\Nand Kirin Toudou for this, too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.26,0:20:30.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It would be great to see this\Nagain during the final, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.52,0:20:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows what's going to happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.37,0:20:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What am I gonna do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.33,0:20:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not a single clue\Nafter all this asking around, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.33,0:20:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll have a look\Nfurther down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.30,0:20:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.67,0:21:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.05,0:21:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The bastard who's been sniffing\Naround here for some reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.68,0:21:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, I'm just looking\Nfor someone, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.10,0:21:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about you come with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.39,0:21:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I really don't have the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.19,0:21:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come back here, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.32,0:21:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard! Where the hell did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.57,0:21:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I go into the alley,\NI'll only get cornered.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.45,0:21:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Guess I'll head back out for now, and—{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.13,0:21:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What should I do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.33,0:21:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't cause a commotion now\Nand risk getting noticed by the perpetrator.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.30,0:21:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.01,0:21:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is someone chasing you, by any chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.35,0:21:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you're in trouble, I can help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.99,0:23:40.04,Next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 19\NBattle Song
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.25,0:23:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What did you think of that, Ayato?\NMy singing...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.12,0:23:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}It's not half bad, wouldn't you say?
